data.description: This is the cutest home at the best price! Gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Atoka with all the bells and whistles! This brick home has a fenced-in backyard, LVP flooring and tile throughout, an updated kitchen with granite countertops, a walk-in laundry room with new pantry shelving, a new heating & air unit in 2020, and a tankless water heater was added in 2020. But wait, there's more...a 15'x25' foot above-ground pool with a multi-level deck around the pool and an attached kids play area.
